{"tid":980301,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"LUNA SEA主音河村隆一患肺腺癌做手術","createTime":"2019-01-13T12:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T03:20:32.000Z","uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0a1962a2a906ce23d4f256c4549ba3a99a98aece","tid":980301,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:01:06.000Z","msg":"東網巨星<br />\n<br />\nLUNA SEA主音河村隆一患肺腺癌做手術<br />\n01月13日(日) 11:06   <br />\nLUNA SEA主音河村隆一透露患上肺腺癌，前日做手術。<br />\nLUNA SEA主音河村隆一透露患上肺腺癌，前日做手術。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n日本搖滾樂隊LUNA SEA的48歲主音河村隆一，今日更新網誌，透露患上肺腺癌，並於前日(11日)入院接受手術切除。<br />\n<br />\n河村隆一在網誌表示：「前陣子發現的，並在11日進行切除手術肺腺癌。」他表示手術後情況良好，他作為歌手，最慶幸肺活量與以前不變。由於癌細胞很小，今後不需要接受放射線治療及服用抗癌劑。河村隆一剛於去年除夕舉行個人跨年演唱會，他手術後會專心休養，而今年是LUNA SEA成軍30周年，5月31日及6月1日將於東京日本武道館開騷。"},{"pid":"99bcb0383c8f9e001df402acfea320b35a5dd146","tid":980301,"uid":186072,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"邊撚個黎"},{"pid":"f1a966ecbf1a26214593e67ff91153db46b21e9b","tid":980301,"uid":18129,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"99bcb0383c8f9e001df402acfea320b35a5dd146","tid":980301,"uid":186072,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"邊撚個黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:11:56.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"2f096a4123f2c1b39dbb785ba3666be1e094aaaf","tid":980301,"uid":18129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:13:21.000Z","msg":"有無報導講係第幾期"},{"pid":"9c95d440b0bd6f3278fbed8afd9f36268b07fd8b","tid":980301,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99bcb0383c8f9e001df402acfea320b35a5dd146","tid":980301,"uid":186072,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"邊撚個黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:14:04.000Z","msg":"LUNA SEA主音呀盲撚"},{"pid":"846f2b7f0504c975e74e741f1d83479d962281ee","tid":980301,"uid":18484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:15:36.000Z","